{
  "name": "PublishObject",
  "summary": "<p><strong>PublishObject</strong> 对象是 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PublishObjects/PublishObjects .htm#PublishObjects.PublishObjects\">PublishObjects</a></strong> 集合的成员。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Workbook/Workbook .htm#Workbook.PublishObjects\">PublishObjects</a></strong>(<em>index</em>)（其中 <em>index</em> 是工作簿中指定项的索引号）可返回一个 <strong>PublishObject</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置第一张工作簿中第一个项的保存位置。本示例假定已经创建PublishObject对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filename</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\example1.html&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿中工作表Sheet1保存到名为 example1.html 的网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublish = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceSheet, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\example1.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>)\n    objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HtmlType</span> = xlHtmlStatic\n    objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Title</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example_PublishObject&quot;</span>\n    objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表保存为网页的工作簿中的项，并可以根据 <strong>PublishObject</strong> 对象中属性和方法所指定的值进行刷新。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "AutoRepublish",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>在保存工作簿时，ET 判断 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PublishObjects/PublishObjects .htm#PublishObjects.PublishObjects\">PublishObjects</a></strong> 集合中的任意一个项目是否具有设置为 <strong>True</strong> 的 <strong>AutoRepublish</strong> 属性。如果有，则重新发布该项目。默认值为 <strong>False</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表上的一个区域发布到E：\\上的一个 HTML 文件中。当用户保存包含该工作表的工作簿时，ET 将自动地将区域重新发布到相同的 HTML 文件中。本示例假定用户能够对网页进行读写访问，并且该工作表中的单元格 A1 到 D10 中都有值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:D10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Book1.xls_130489&quot;</span>)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoRepublish</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作簿添加一个 PublishObject 对象，并显示对象的 AutoRepublish 属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:C10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoRepublish</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DivID",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回用于标识网页上 HTML &lt;DIV&gt; 标记的唯一标识符。此标记与保存为网页的文档中的某一项相关联。该项可以是整个工作簿、一张工作表、选定的打印区域、自动筛选区域、单元格区域、图表、数据透视表或查询表。<strong>String</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例先在活动工作簿上新建 PublishObject 对象并保存到网页，然后从该网页 &lt;DIV&gt; 标记中获取标识符，并在名为D:\\\\example1.html的网页（通过保存某个工作簿得到的）中查找该行。然后，此示例还创建该网页的一个副本（D:\\\\example1.html），并在该副本的 &lt;DIV&gt; 标记前插入一个注释行。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObjects = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>\n    publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\example1.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;$C$2:$C$6&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic)\n    publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> strTargetDivID = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DivID</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> f1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FreeFile</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Open</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\example1.html&quot;</span>, f1, jsInput)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> (!<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">EOF</span>(f1)) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> str = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LineInput</span>(f1)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (str.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">includes</span>(strTargetDivID) &amp;&amp; str.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">includes</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&lt;div&quot;</span>)) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&lt;!--Saved item--&gt;&quot;</span>)\n        }\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(str)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Close</span>(f1)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作簿上新建PublishObject对象并保存到网页，然后显示该工作簿上所有PublishObject对象的&lt;DIV&gt;标记中的唯一标识符。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObjects = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>\n    publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceSheet, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\example1.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>)\n    publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublish = publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DivID</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Filename",
      "summary": "<p>如果指定路径中的文件夹不存在，则 <strong>FileName</strong> 属性将产生一个错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置保存指定源对象位置的 URL（Intranet 或网站上）或路径（本地或网络）。<strong>String</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向活动工作簿添加一个 PublishObject 对象，并设置保存活动工作簿中第一项的位置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:C10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filename</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Server\\\\Stockreport.html&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作簿添加一个 PublishObject 对象，并显示对象的 Filename 属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:C10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filename</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "HtmlType",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>XlHtmlType</strong> 可为以下<strong>XlHtmlType</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>xlHtmlCalc</strong> 使用电子表格组件。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlHtmlChart</strong> 使用图表组件。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlHtmlList</strong> 使用数据透视表组件。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlHtmlStatic</strong> 静态（非交互式）HTML 仅用于查看。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置在将指定项保存到网页中时，由 ET 所生成的 HTML 的类型。可以为下表中列出的 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlHtmlType 枚举.html\">XlHtmlType</a></strong> 常量之一，用于指定该项在网页中是静态还是可交互的。默认值为 <strong>xlHtmlStatic</strong>。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿中工作表“First Quarter”上的区域 D5:D9 保存到名为 Stockreport.html 的网页，并判断如果项目保存到网页时 ET 生成的 HTML 类型为xlHtmlStatic，则通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Server\\\\Stockreport.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;First Quarter&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;$D$5:$D$9&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Book1_4170&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HtmlType</span> == xlHtmlStatic) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;项目保存到网页时 ET 生成的 HTML 类型为xlHtmlStatic&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoRepublish</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作簿添加一个 PublishObject 对象，并显示对象的 HtmlType 属性值是否为 xlHtmlStatic。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Server\\\\Stockreport.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;First Quarter&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;$D$5:$D$9&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HtmlType</span> == xlHtmlStatic)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlHtmlType",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Sheet",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PublishObject/PublishObject .htm#PublishObject.PublishObject\">PublishObject</a></strong> 对象的工作表名称。只读 <strong>String</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例确定工作表的名称，假定该工作表包含在网页中保存为静态 HTML 的第一个PublishObject对象。然后，示例将Boolean变量blnSheetFound设置为True。如果文档中没有任何项保存为静态 HTML，则blnSheetFound为False。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> blnSheetFound = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> poSheet = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublish = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HtmlType</span> == xlHtmlStatic) {\n            poSheet = objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheet</span>\n            blnSheetFound = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作簿上创建新的 PublishObject 对象，然后将第一张工作簿上所有 PublishObject 对象保存到网页并显示其工作表名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\示例1\\\\example.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;$A$1:$A$10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example_test&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublish = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheet</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Source",
      "summary": "<p>如果 <strong>SourceType</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>xlSourceRange</strong>，则此属性返回一个区域，该区域可以是一个定义名称。如果 <strong>SourceType</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>xlSourceChart</strong>、<strong>xlSourcePivotTable</strong> 或 <strong>xlSourceQuery</strong>，则此属性返回对象的名称，例如：图表名称、数据透视表名称或查询表名称。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个代表唯一名称的 <strong>Variant</strong> 值，该名称用于标识其 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PublishObject/PublishObject .htm#PublishObject.SourceType\">SourceType</a></strong> 属性值为 <strong>xlSourceRange</strong>、<strong>xlSourceChart</strong>、<strong>xlSourcePrintArea</strong>、<strong>xlSourceAutoFilter</strong>、<strong>xlSourcePivotTable</strong> 或 <strong>xlSourceQuery</strong> 的项。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例确定保存为网页的第一张图表（在第一个工作簿中）的唯一名称，然后将Boolean型的变量blnChartFound设置为True。如果文档中没有保存为图表组件的项，则blnChartFound为False。本示例假定已经创建PublishObject对象*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> blnSheetFound = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> poSource = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublish = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceType</span> == xlSourceChart) {\n            poSource = objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Soursce</span>\n            blnSheetFound = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作簿上新建 PublishObject 对象，并将第一张工作簿上所有 PublishObject 对象的 Source 属性值赋值给单元格，然后将所有 PublishObject 对象保存到网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceQuery, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\示例1\\\\example.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ExternalData_1&quot;</span>, xlHtmlChart, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example_test&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublish = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Cells</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Source</span>\n        objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "SourceType",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSourceType 枚举.html\">XlSourceType</a></strong> 值，它代表所发布项目的类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例确定保存为网页的第一张图表（在第一个工作簿中）的唯一名称，然后将Boolean型的变量blnChartFound设置为True。如果文档中没有保存为图表组件的项，则blnChartFound为False。本示例假定已经创建PublishObject对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> blnSheetFound = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> poSource = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublish = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceType</span> == xlSourceChart) {\n            poSource = objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Soursce</span>\n            blnSheetFound = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作簿上新建 PublishObject 对象，并判断如果第一张工作簿上PublishObject对象的类型为xlSourceQuery，则通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceQuery, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\示例1\\\\example.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ExternalData_1&quot;</span>, xlHtmlChart, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example_test&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublish = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceType</span> == xlSourceQuery) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`第<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${i}</span>个PublishObject对象的类型为xlSourceQuery`</span>)\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlSourceType",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Title",
      "summary": "<p>在 Web 浏览器中查看文档时，标题通常显示在窗口的标题栏中。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置在将文档另存为网页时的网页标题。<strong>String</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿中工作表“Sheet1”上的区域 B1:C10 保存到名为 Work1.html 的网页，并将网页标题设置为“Sales Forecast”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work1.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:C10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Title</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sales Forecast&quot;</span>\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿中工作表“Sheet1”上的区域 A1:D10 保存到名为 Work.html 的网页，并显示网页的标题。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:D10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Book1.xls_130489&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Test&quot;</span>)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Title</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作簿添加一个 PublishObject 对象，然后判断如果该对象的 HtmlType 属性值为xlHtmlStatic，则删除该对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:C10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HtmlType</span> == xlHtmlStatic) {\n        publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向活动工作簿添加一个 PublishObject 对象，然后删除该对象，最后显示当前剩余 PublishObject 对象的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:B10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Publish",
      "summary": "<p><strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PublishObject/PublishObject .htm#PublishObject.Filename\">FileName</a></strong> 属性可返回或设置 HTML 文件的位置和文件名。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>将文档中的项或项的集合保存到网页中。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿中工作表“First Quarter”上的区域 D5:D9 保存到名为 Stockreport.html 的网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Server\\\\Stockreport.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;First Quarter&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;$D$5:$D$9&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Book2_25082&quot;</span>)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoRepublish</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作簿添加一个 PublishObject 对象，并判断如果对象的 HtmlType 属性值为 xlHtmlStatic，则将第一张工作簿中工作表“Sheet1”上的区域 B1:C10 保存到名为 Work.html 的网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:C10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HtmlType</span> == xlHtmlStatic) {\n        publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Create",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>在 HTML 文件存在的情况下，如果该值为 <strong>True</strong>，则会替换该文件；如果该值为 <strong>False</strong>，则会在文件末尾插入这些项。如果文件不存在，则不论 <em>Create</em> 参数的值如何，都会创建文件。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
